    "html": "<div class=\"newsitem\"><h1>Entelect</h1><div class=\"newsdate\"><span class=\"day\"> Thursday </span><span class=\"date\"> 30 </span><span class=\"month\">August</span><span class=\"year\">2018</span></div><p>Two Stellenbosch University undergraduate teams placed 3rd and 4th in Entelect’s <em>Challenge, University Cup</em>.</p><p>The two Stellenbosch teams were made up of a mixture of students from CS and Engineering.</p><h3 id=\"info\">Info</h3><ul><li>A full description of the challenge can be found <a href=\"https://challenge.entelect.co.za/university\">here</a> and,</li><li>The leaderboard can be found <a href=\"https://challenge.entelect.co.za/university/leaderboard\">here</a>.</li></ul><h3 id=\"the-teams-members\">The teams members:</h3><ul><li>Team “🤔🤔🤔”: Matthew Baas, Kevin Eloff, and Raynhardt van Zyl.</li><li>Team “SplitPhase”:Luke Joshua, Joseph Rautenbach, and Mari-Louise Bouwer.</li></ul></div>\n",
    "sections": [
      {
        "key": "000-main",
        "slot": "main",
        "html": "<div class=\"newsitem\"><h1>Entelect</h1><div class=\"newsdate\"><span class=\"day\"> Thursday </span><span class=\"date\"> 30 </span><span class=\"month\">August</span><span class=\"year\">2018</span></div><p>Two Stellenbosch University undergraduate teams placed 3rd and 4th in Entelect’s <em>Challenge, University Cup</em>.</p><p>The two Stellenbosch teams were made up of a mixture of students from CS and Engineering.</p><h3 id=\"info\">Info</h3><ul><li>A full description of the challenge can be found <a href=\"https://challenge.entelect.co.za/university\">here</a> and,</li><li>The leaderboard can be found <a href=\"https://challenge.entelect.co.za/university/leaderboard\">here</a>.</li></ul><h3 id=\"the-teams-members\">The teams members:</h3><ul><li>Team “🤔🤔🤔”: Matthew Baas, Kevin Eloff, and Raynhardt van Zyl.</li><li>Team “SplitPhase”:Luke Joshua, Joseph Rautenbach, and Mari-Louise Bouwer.</li></ul></div>\n"
      }
    ]
